{
  "stem": "833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She would have-- would have to be chaperoned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was one of the chaperones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she decided she wanted to go to that very famous ball, Kunst Haus, where they-- they-- big exhibitions are in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's always a ball in February.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she decided with two of her friends, young-- young girls-- she goes and she asks me to-- to be her chaperone.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 23.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and the day before, she got ill, my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she says, Herbert, these two girls, they already made their costumes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Would you go with them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they wouldn't be allowed either to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went with them, took a book with me because I wasn't dancing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't doing anything like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went in there and sat down in the corner and told the girls, go and have fun.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And every 30 minutes, you come here and say you're all right just that I know what you're doing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was about half an hour that I was sitting there looking at my book, and I saw three people coming in, two girls and one boy, who had the fantastic costume.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were not costumed but seemingly came from somewhere where they were dressed up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I saw this little girl just arranging her hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I saw those hands doing-- I was electrified by the-- by the movement and by the hair and by the way she moved.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was tiny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was about 4-- 4'9'-- 4-- yeah, 4'9'.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She didn't grow very much since then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's funny.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But any-- anyway, I approached her immediately and asked her if she would dance with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was of course-- And she started dancing with me, and she started laughing at me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you ever dance?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
